title: Out Of Luck
itunes:title: Out Of Luck
description:
Colin discusses the shocking news of Andrew Luck retiring, the impact it will have on the league, his new NFL predictions, and where he was right and wrong over the weekend. Guests include Jay Glazer, David Shaw, Pat McAfee, and Antonio Cromartie.
